Encapsulation:-->
	=> The meaning of Encapsulation, is to make sure that 
		"sensitive" data is hidden from users
		
	=> Encapsulation is also usefull to bind method and 
		variable data as single unit
		
	=> During Encapsulation we decleare variable with private 
		modifier and using setter and getter methods
	    we can retrive publicly any where in the project.
		
			
			
		Advantages:-->
			=> protect data from unknown users
			=> data flexible
			=> Reusable Data
			
			